personalInfo.title: JSON-based resume design studio for IT professionals
personalInfo.bio:
Status: ‚óè Online | v0.2.0
You are about to use cre8ive.cv ‚Äì a free tool for generating a highly customizable resume. Its data layer is just a pure JSON object which can be exported and reimported. Why developers love it?
  • Flexibility: Go beyond themes. Use custom HTML in any field ‚Äì the final look depends only on your cre8ivity !
  • Convenience: Real-time WYSIWYG interface with no user account needed
  • Privacy focused: Client-side data storage (no personal data is stored on the server after PDF rendering)
/* Any feedback? The project is vibe coded so bugs are possible. In order to contact the author use the links above or create an issue on the GitHub repository.*/

skills.name: Features
items: All your data in a single exportable JSON object
Optional photo is a part of the JSON (encoded as base64)
Export to PDF, HTML and JSON
Custom HTML support
No personal data is stored on the server
Uses localStorage. Update is made after each change
You don't need to save your progress. It's kept until you overwrite it
Even if you close the browser or restart the computer
Optional watermark to support the project
Gallery of templates to start with
Your resume can be version-controlled with Git
üí° Protip: You can combine your cre8ivity with AI to boost your HTML customizations
